Revision history for App-BashCompletionF

0.03    2014-10-31 (PERLANCAR)

	- No functional changes.

	- Tweak output message to be clearer.


0.02    2014-10-31 (PERLANCAR)

        [ENHANCEMENTS]

        - Add subcommand: remove-all.

        - Subcommands remove and add-pc now accept multiple arguments.

        - Subcommand add-all-pc can now accept dirs (but still defaults to PATH
          if none are specified).

        - Observe DEBUG environment variable.


0.01    2014-10-31 (PERLANCAR)

        - First release.
